                    <span>While this book is one sided, to blame the Tamils for the Sri Lankan violence is propaganda.  I have known people from Sri Lanka who use Dharma talks to promote violence.   Not that the Tamils are innocent either, but it is full hearty to think that the Buddhist community is univerally peaceful.  As a someone who has studied and been around Buddhist culture most of his life, I find the over idealization of the Dharma disturbing and can lead to dangerous justifications of various actions in Buddhist history. I encourage people to read this book for that reason. </span>
                  
